WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.060
Here is the question. Explain

2
00:00:03.060 --> 00:00:06.120
how to throw away inorganic waste.

3
00:00:06.120 --> 00:00:08.559
Let's learn the answer.

4
00:00:08.559 --> 00:00:10.997
There are three easy steps.

5
00:00:10.997 --> 00:00:13.627
Step one. Pick up the debris

6
00:00:13.627 --> 00:00:16.257
and put it in a trash bag.

7
00:00:16.257 --> 00:00:18.982
Step two. Tie the trash

8
00:00:18.982 --> 00:00:21.708
bag tightly so nothing falls out.

9
00:00:21.708 --> 00:00:24.911
Step three. Take the trash bag

10
00:00:24.911 --> 00:00:28.115
to the assigned waste disposal area.

11
00:00:28.115 --> 00:00:31.557
Remember. Bag it, tie it, take it

12
00:00:31.557 --> 00:00:35.000
to the disposal area. Well done Caleb!


